My thought it is the waterpumpbearing, almost for sure. My 2000 Sporting did
it also now and again. My Fiat-dealer had a look at it and they put some
drops of diesel in  the coolingsystem to grease the pump-bearing (it's not
allowed, but it worked fine!!). If you don't want to do that then you'll
have to take the pump out and repair it, if you can repair it at all these
days. Lots of success!
Greetings, E-Cie.
